   ''title row'': type title - OR - leave row __empty__ to accept "<$text text={{$:/state/SideEditor}}/>"<br>
   ''tags row'': type tags and [&zwj;[bracketed tags]&zwj;] - OR - leave row __empty__<br>
   ''text'' ...
</td>
</tr>
</table>

</div>
</$list>
</$navigator>",
